@startuml
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
participant "Auth Service\n(Supabase)" as AuthService
participant "Email Service" as Email
actor "User" as User

== Pha 5: Gửi email xác nhận thanh toán ==

note over PaymentService: Local event handler xử lý\nSubscriptionPurchasedEvent
activate PaymentService

PaymentService -> AuthService: getProfile(userId)\nLấy email và tên người dùng
activate AuthService
AuthService --> PaymentService: Trả về fullName & email
deactivate AuthService

PaymentService -> Email: sendPaymentSuccessEmail\n(fullName, email, plan, periodEnd)
activate Email
Email --> PaymentService: Gửi mail thành công
deactivate Email

PaymentService --> User: Email thông báo thanh toán thành công
deactivate PaymentService
@enduml
